description:
Karen Bassie's short study of the creator Gods of the Maya presents the basics of the Mayan beliefs that were accepted as standards across the Mayan civilization. Mainly drawn from the Popol Vuh, this work details the 3 generations of classical Mayan deities. Also detailed is the way these Gods relate to their calender.


